properties.remarks: Border Area. Flights are allowed only with the permission of the Police and Border Guard Board. To fly in the area, a permit shall be requested at the e-mail address ppa@politsei.ee. The limit does not extend if flight safety requires it.The Defence Forces, Police and Border Guard Board, Internal Security Service, Tax and Customs Board, Rescue Board and Environmental Board do not need to apply for a permit to fly in the area. The aforementioned authorities must notify the Police and Border Guard Board of their intention to fly, if possible, at least 60 minutes before the flight takes place.

Flights are allowed only with the permission of the Environmental Board.
